63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z"></path></svg></div></div><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Impulsa la Eficiencia</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Reduzca las llamadas entrantes y la administración manual con autoservicio para citas, registros y pagos.</p></div></div><div class="text-center space-y-3"><div class="flex justify-center"><div class="w-16 h-16 bg-teal-primary/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-heart h-8 w-8 text-teal-primary" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2 9.5a5.5 5.5 0 0 1 9.591-3.676.56.56 0 0 0 .818 0A5.49 5.49 0 0 1 22 9.5c0 2.29-1.5 4-3 5.5l-5.492 5.313a2 2 0 0 1-3 .019L5 15c-1.5-1.5-3-3.2-3-5.5"></path></svg></div></div><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Fortalece la Participación</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Las notificaciones push y las integraciones de dispositivos de salud fomentan una mejor adherencia a los planes de atención.</p></div></div><div class="text-center space-y-3"><div class="flex justify-center"><div class="w-16 h-16 bg-teal-primary/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-users h-8 w-8 text-teal-primary" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><path d="M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744"></path><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle></svg></div></div><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Apoya Su Marca</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Elija entre la aplicación gratuita de ContinuousCare o su propia aplicación con marca personalizada, publicada bajo el nombre de su consultorio o startup.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center transition-all duration-700 opacity-0 translate-y-10"><div class="lg:w-full space-y-8"><div class="inline-block"><span class="bg-green-success/20 text-green-success px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-green-success/30">Atención Multimodal</span></div><div><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-6 leading-tight">Atención Multimodal</h2><p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">Proporcione atención a través de cada canal que prefieran sus pacientes, todo accesible dentro de la aplicación.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-calendar h-6 w-6 text-green-success flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M8 2v4"></path><path d="M16 2v4"></path><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="4" rx="2"></rect><path d="M3 10h18"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Consultas Presenciales</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Los pacientes reservan y se registran con facilidad.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-message-square h-6 w-6 text-green-success flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 17a2 2